# Planning 
UniWell health tracker that supports SDG3: Good Health and Well-Being.

# Problem statement
Students find it challenging to track daily health habits and respond to emergencies quickly.

# Objective
Our objective is to provide a daily haelth logging for instance water intake, sleep, exercise and meal.
UniWell will enable student to log their daily health, reminders and access emergency support when needed.
This promotes healthier life style and timely medical attention.

# Scope
The system will include:
- Authentication: Secure login, Create a password, Password reset.
- Health Records: Input and update daily water intake, sleep hours, exercise, and meals.
- Data Visualization: Dashboard summaries and weekly averages.
- Smart Reminders: Notifications when data is not recorded.
- Admin Functions: Account management, health tips publishing, statistical reporting, and system monitoring.

# Timeline
- Week 1: Planning and requirements.
- Week 2: Design(wireframes and diagrams).
- Week 3: Prototype development.
- Week 4: Testing and Finalization.

